{
  "stem": "5103.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--brought SS guards and other people into the house.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Do you remember feeling danger from Anna or--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, Anna was always very angry, actually.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's how I saw it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She used to say, how can you do this to me?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "How can you do this to me?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, you know the situation we are in.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the daughter used to just sort of ignore the fact of that, I think, because she used to shout back at her mother.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I don't know what she used to say.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But I think she felt that while she could get money, and while she could get lovely-- she, I remember, always had lots of nice clothes on.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And she used to look like quite a nice, groomed person.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And in the war, I don't think that was easy to come by.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I'm sure that, you know, it was one of those things that had to be done in order to keep yourself looking groomed and, and up-to-date, with nylon stockings.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "God knows what they had in those days.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So this one day, she heard-- I heard noises, shouting, noise, and commotion.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she-- Anna came out and said, look, come quickly.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Come quickly.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You have to do this.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I said, yes, yes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And she said, look now.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "See this piano here?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Now, in the bottom-- and she opened up, and in the bottom it was an old fashioned piano, upright piano.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was a-- you open up where the pedals are there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there was like a big cavity, big enough for a child to get into.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there was a panel in front of it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now, she said Corrie, you have to lie down in there.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
